OL,7,FIn order to tackle a problem, it is
OL,8,Fsensible to try and establish its
OL,9,Fscale. After all, any crackdown on the
OL,10,Famount of untreated sewage entering the
OL,11,Fnation's rivers would risk being
OL,12,Frendered meaningless without knowing
OL,13,Fjust how much filth is swilling into
OL,14,Four waterways in the first place.
OL,16,FThat, sadly, is at risk of being the
OL,17,Fcase when it comes to the efforts of
OL,18,Fthe regulators charged with the care of
OL,19,Four rivers to ascertain the levels of
OL,20,F"foul water" being released with grim
OL,21,Fregularity in Britain.
OL,3,CWhy is there filth swilling into our
OL,4,Cwaterways? Under-investment and
OL,5,Cunder-enforcement
